name: Skirt mounts
description:
Mountains are protectors of our village, and all the villages next to us. This part of desert is a bit colder because of the mountains that surrounds it, therefore you can see a lot of gardens and greens  unlike the other cities in desert.
These mountains are my grandpa's favorite. A wide chain, with a lot of horizontal wrinkles, ending here with a perfect final curve.  All of these details made the people call it the skirt mount since long time ago. It looks exactly like a wide short skirt.From our balcony, we can see edges of this skirt. 
---
35mm black and white photography
